        <updateDate>2023-11-24T17:01:33Z</updateDate>
        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Helping Invest in Key Environments Act or the HIKE Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill adjusts the boundary of the Santa Monica Mountains National Recreation Area in California to include the Rim of the Valley Corridor.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Utility or water resource facility activities in the corridor must be conducted in a manner that reasonably avoids or reduces the impact of the activities on the corridor's resources.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
